{"tid":201650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲人地鐵突暴打中國人，辱：「中國騙子！」","createTime":"2017-04-15T02:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T02:35:58.000Z","uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c84267cadc00abc0fb82065a207f46976fdc8ab0","tid":201650,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:27:21.000Z","msg":"Twitter近日有一則視頻瘋傳。視頻中一名乘客在墨爾本火車上突然侮辱一名疑為華人的乘客，稱其為「中國騙子」，引起網民熱議。墨爾本火車營運商及維多利亞省警方目前正在進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n英國《每日郵報》報導，事件發生於墨爾本內城北部的South Morang線，視頻是由一位乘客拍攝的。<br />\n<br />\n視頻裡面見到，該男子吼叫道「你想要幹嘛？」，然後開始充滿侮辱性言辭，並對其進行種族主義攻擊，稱其為「中國騙子」。儘管這名男性被他的女性朋友拉住並要他鎮定，但他卻繼續侮辱該名顯然是亞裔的男子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n然後，該男子在Northcote站下車，但他下車後仍在對門口大聲辱罵，：「你這個騙子！」，更警告其他乘客不應該支持他(亞裔男子)。<br />\n<br />\n墨爾本列車方正在調查這一事件，維省警方也已經介入。"},{"pid":"69c48a8ae6e25420901e323fc22a56625a6a5afa","tid":201650,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:29:42.000Z","msg":"拔草測風向，免得跟車太貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed7a9264fb065417361fe2f024e815f7a2ec95b","tid":201650,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:31:17.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe2eff82775d4677d5d18d766eb09ff7224b2059","tid":201650,"uid":29851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:32:04.000Z","msg":"暴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d8d394905dd4a7e1f40b90d39f9edb59b5b40e","tid":201650,"uid":52949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:32:08.000Z","msg":"討厭中國人的外國人開始行動了"},{"pid":"8fea14f0d21455117c4be4f2d5ef4cdf3f34823d","tid":201650,"uid":10937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:32:46.000Z","msg":"要用正確方式打擊支那蝗蟲，請參考美國德州個間大學，支那賊無地自容，淨係識得9叫人歧視佢，除左學校所謂會處理下，仲有邊d人撐支那賊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47f57c908c1643d5beaf982dd856ed41cd3eb7f","tid":201650,"uid":10937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"而家你用左暴力打支那賊就係蝕章做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b89cc94e697a25ffe8b65c6c158248813de38b","tid":201650,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T02:35:58.000Z","msg":"視頻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}